    "long_instructions": "## Reference\r\n\r\nUse AI Chat to help design a new building. \r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. **Copy and paste** the prompt below into AI Chat. Press **Send** and read AI Chat's response. \r\n\r\n>You are an architect planning a building downtown. Figure out how many shops can fit on the ground floor of the new building, which is the size of a football field.\r\n\r\n2. Add a **reference** to your prompt by:\r\n    - Uploading a blueprint of the building from the Library\r\n    - Finding your own reference to upload\r\n3. Revise your prompt to AI Chat by adding in **Reference**. Press **Send** and read AI Chat's response. \r\n4. Find and complete the section in your Unit Guide called \"Reference\". \r\n\r\n**Try it out!**\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n::: details [**Not sure what reference to add?**]\r\nTry copy and pasting the following revised prompt into AI Chat: \r\n>You are an architect planning a building downtown. Look at the blueprint attached and figure out how many shops can fit on the ground floor of the new building, which is the size of a football field.\r\n:::",
